title: Klaus Schulze & Rainer Bloss - Drive Inn Vol.2 (New age)
description:
Re-seed of someone else&#039;s torrent I downloaded some months ago.

It&#039;s Rainer Bloss&#039; album "Drive Inn II" which has some really interesting tracks. Better than "part 1" I think, but this time Klaus Schulze is producer only.

2 Dessert Inn (4:31)

Hard to find on CD? Rather impossible I would say.
